uk.ac.ed.epcc.webapp.jdbc.expr

Class DistinctCountSQLValue

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.ed.epcc.webapp.jdbc.expr.DistinctCountSQLValue
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    GroupingSQLValue<DistinctCount>, SQLValue<DistinctCount>, Targetted<DistinctCount>

    public class DistinctCountSQLValue
extends java.lang.Object
implements GroupingSQLValue<DistinctCount>
    A SQLValue that generates an DistinctCount This is intended to be used in group by queries in conjunction with a group-by clause on the nested GroupingSQLValue. The SQL fragment is therefore the same as the nested value but the result in wrapped in a DistinctCount
